title: The Science of High-Wire Stunts with Philippe Petit
description: Put on your safety harness as Neil deGrasse Tyson investigates the world of death defying stunts with high-wire artist Philippe Petit, co-host Eugene Mirman, and guests Charles Liu, tight-rope instructor Sonja Harpstead, and Bill Nye the Science Guy.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
